You are here: SALESFORCE HELP DOCS INSURANCE Vlocity Insurance Application Suite Winter '22 Minor Release 234.1

This section describes key fixes and enhancements for the Vlocity Insurance Application Suite in this minor release.

Property and Casualty Application for Vlocity Insurance Application Suite 234.1
All new commercial products for quoting and rating, a harmonized property claims process, and brand new claims dashboards to see what needs your attention.
Group Voluntary Benefits Application for Vlocity Insurance Application Suite 234.1
New products that offer additional plans to employees, the option to enable bulk enrollment for up to 500 members, and more.
